des:
Math Practice gives you daily exercises for addition, subtraction, multiplication and division. Just open Math Practice, and follow the prompt to choose the operation you'd like to work on. You can practice for as long as you'd like!

The skill has been refined through extensive testing for accuracy and precision in listening to responses. It's perfect to keep your mind sharp and to master basic math! Try it out and see the results!
